{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_halo_set_1", "eventName": "實驗進行中", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "實驗進行中", "storyInfo": "埃琳娜因違反實驗室安全規定而收到防衛科的責任認定書。能量科斐爾迪南主任此時敲響了實驗室的門，一場針對她的“實驗”開始了。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“萊茵防衛科責任認定報告：實習研究員埃琳娜·烏比卡......”", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“違反實驗室操作指南，違反研究員生命安全守則，違反防衛科救援方案......”", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“擅自返回源石液洩漏事故中心區，重啟已被放棄的實驗反應裝置......”", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“打亂防衛科既定救援程序，導致救援難度上升......”", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜倒吸一口涼氣。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......完了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "防衛科發來的責任書都送到我手上了，塞雷婭主任那種性格......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我要被炒魷魚了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜看了看實驗室四周。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾人合用的空間一角堆放著她的器械和儀器，桌面上攤著她沒有寫完的報告，還有昨天剩下的半袋提神劑。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......太可惜了，這可是我的第一個大型實驗，還沒得出個結果就......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且姐姐遲早也會知道的，她肯定又要為我擔心了......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但還是做好準備吧......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#4$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她嘆了口氣，放下了手中的報告，開始收拾起桌面上自己的東西，一件一件整齊地放進包中。"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南主任......！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（怎麼主任都來了？事情鬧大了......？）", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實習研究員......埃琳娜·烏比卡？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主任，我這個級別的實驗應該不需要您親自來......？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜，你的數據現在是多少？", "name": "萊茵實驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......1.39，還是沒動......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼回事啊，第二十三天了，其他數據一點問題都沒有，按理來說上周就該出結果了，到現在一點反應都沒有！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "急死我了......！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小丫頭，過來喝杯茶吧？", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，沃利......我喝不下去......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者這樣，我教你個好辦法。你把這個寫了，就不會著急了。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是什麼......“實驗項目申請報告”？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我寫這個幹什麼啊！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓你別再盯著這個已經被項目半放棄的實驗啊。不如好好想想你下一個實驗要做什麼、怎麼做出結果，再把它做好。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看我，上班先喝一杯茶，上個實驗失敗了就立馬開始推進下一個想法，這才是正常的狀態。我們是在做研究，誰能次次都成功呢？", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜，你要是真的擔心斐爾迪南把你開了，你就別再死磕眼前這個了，他不會在乎這一個實驗怎麼樣的。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只會說，“萊茵每天有上千個實驗在推進，我只在乎最後的結果”。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噗，你學得好像。", "name": "萊茵實驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這個實驗不是之前那種性質的......它是B25項目的基礎數據實驗，是我加入的第一個大項目，我付出了多少努力才搶到的！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它對我來說太重要了，我不能就這樣放棄這次參與大項目的機會......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是真做好了後續補救方案，你放棄了這一個不會怎麼樣的，最多會被他當面罵一頓......", "name": "萊茵實驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（打了個冷顫）", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒和斐爾迪南主任接洽過呢，看起來能量科每個人都很怕他？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#4$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和他說過一次話就知道了，他誇你比罵你還讓人難受。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你還選擇來能量科？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#4$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......因為不得不承認，他確實厲害。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要跟過一次他直接負責的項目，能得到的進步堪比自己一個人研究多少年。只是能被他看上的人少之又少，一年都不一定有一個。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是這裡大多數人選擇來能量科的理由，難道你不是？", "name": "萊茵實驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實是啦。我大學時就聽說過他的很多成果，猜他肯定是一個很厲害的人，來能量科肯定能實現我的夢想。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且他這種頂尖的人，有點奇怪脾氣，也很正常吧？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哼。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜一撐胳膊，從桌子上撐起身子。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，我肯定能找出這個實驗的問題。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可是我的第一個實驗，還是B25項目的基礎數據，我好不容易才搶到這個機會的！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是被家裡那兩個老古板知道了，又會覺得讓我遵守他們的決定才是對的，要我去做家裡那套糊弄人的東西......姐姐也會擔心我......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就不信了！怎麼可能，難道它還真的出不了結果？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就加油吧，充滿幹勁的小傢伙，我祝你成功......", "name": "萊茵實驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘀——嘀——嘀——"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......什麼聲音？是警報器在響嗎？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，是什麼出問題了？溫度？濕度？我去調數值。", "name": "萊茵實驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“室內源石濃度”......？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？！", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜猛地站起，直奔基地警報裝置。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼回事？實驗室源石濃度超出了警報值！是源石液洩漏了？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_warning"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快走，把防護面具戴上！", "name": "萊茵實驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "防衛科嗎？這裡是013號實驗基地，內部環境源石濃度超標，推測發生源石液洩漏！已經拉下警報通知人員撤離，需要防衛科支援！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，013號實驗基地，源石濃度已超標，不清楚洩漏源，需要支援！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以發現源石濃度超標後，我馬上去拉響警報，向防衛科上報情況，通知基地內人員撤離。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我中止了實驗，也封閉了易反應原料，爭取把後續問題處理難度降到最低，我還通知了外包人員和拓荒者基地。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這是我在萊茵的第一個項目，所以後來我就......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是我要聽的。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#7$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南的視線掃過埃琳娜已經收拾了大半的桌面。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在收拾東西？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只有七分鐘留給你，放下東西，先看這個。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......數據報告？結果這麼快就出來了！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主任，它是很有價值的數據嗎？是很重要嗎？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並沒有。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很好地浪費了我給你的資源，並讓防衛科的責任書塞滿了我的郵箱。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你能記清楚牆上寫的每一條安全須知。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......很抱歉主任，我並沒有在規定時間內拿出實驗數據結果。我會整理好剩下的部分，交接給下一個負責人。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......因為我的失誤導致項目延期的有關問題，我也會去找項目負責人儘快處理，盡我最大的努力挽回損失。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都可以。我不在乎這個。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想知道的是你返回實驗室的原因。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為那個時候我好像聽到了什麼......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g2_edgeofbase", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘀——嘀——嘀——"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（剛剛我絕對聽到了什麼......我實驗反應的指示表響了......？）", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於出來了，天啊......這次事故得開掉多少人啊......", "name": "萊茵實驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（是它終於開始反應了嗎......？）", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這下好了，埃琳娜，你是真的不用擔心自己的實驗結果怎麼樣了。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在看來，基地裡的所有項目估計都會延期。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼回事啊！你們都在幹什麼？", "name": "慌張的拓荒者"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沃利......之前有出現過在異常環境下實驗反而成功的情況吧？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有啊，我們通常把它叫作“真理的眷顧”。運氣好了，總會有那麼一兩回。", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等下，你再幫我看一下我的防護面具有沒有戴好，我還是有點擔心......", "name": "萊茵實驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不行......）", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我肯定是聽到了，我的實驗正在反應！）", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "撤到這裡足夠安全了嗎？我們要不要再走遠點？我們不去安全屋嗎？", "name": "慌張的外包人員"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這群瘋子......！我們會因此被感染......這完全不符當初簽下的合約！", "name": "慌張的外包人員"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，還活著就行，起碼這次還有個小姑娘願意通知一下你逃跑。", "name": "冷漠的拓荒者"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......等等，喂......你們有看見埃琳娜嗎......？她怎麼不在這裡？", "name": "萊茵實驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘀——！嘀——！嘀——！"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜撲到自己的桌前。"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空無一人的實驗室中，警報和指示表的提示音混雜在一起，源石濃度已經攀升到了一個極易致人感染的數值。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為人們慌張離去而有些雜亂的實驗台上，已經被放棄的實驗卻在源石液洩漏的環境下開始快速反應，指示表瘋狂擺動。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彷彿是想把過去的時間裡未出現的結果全部展示出一般，一旁的終端顯示器快速閃出數條實驗數據，警示燈閃爍不止。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......果然！咳，我沒聽錯！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然，果然！咳咳......它動了！出結果了！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來不及扯來被踢開的椅子，埃琳娜半跪在桌前，極快地記錄著一條條數據。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讀數1.97，我需要把它帶入這個公式，導出結果......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "環境濃度......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儲存......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰還在裡面？", "name": "防衛科成員"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-30", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜俯下身子，沉默不語，加快了記錄的速度。"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片區域已經清空完畢，誰還在裡面？", "name": "防衛科成員"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......救援目標方位已確認，確認為遺漏人員。", "name": "防衛科成員"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來不及了，最後一行......！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......它是我參與的第一個項目，我很重視它。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#4$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時候我發現它終於開始反應了，我猜測是我之前為實驗提供的環境太理想化，並沒有達到反應進行的必要條件。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#4$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它在高源石濃度環境下得到的結果絕對值得我去記錄，哪怕是一個異常數據，也肯定能為以後的實驗提供支持。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算沒有結果，我也要去確認。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以......我回去了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還剩四分鐘。你講完了？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是一個很特殊的理由。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，你拿到報告之後問我的第一句話是什麼？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“它是很有價值的數據嗎？”", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它不是。你現在會再去搶它嗎？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......會的，主任。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理由是？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想放棄我努力了這麼長時間的成果。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......雖然它已經被大家放棄了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我已經付出了這麼久的努力，我沒想那麼多......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它在那種環境下觸發了反應，很有可能就是一條全新的數據或者公式，那就是我的成果。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我搶出來了，我就能更進一步，可以繼續自己的實驗，或者是更進一步做更核心的內容......而且，說不定呢，我覺得我能成功！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停，不要浪費時間，你不需要告訴我這麼多。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南指向窗外。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個基地有無數個像你這樣的實驗員，他們身上有著無數令旁人讚頌的特質，聰穎、果決、領導力......這些人每天能產出多少噸廢紙？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當這些成為普遍擁有的特質時，它們就是最普通的。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能做出搶數據的決定，不錯，但還不夠。我並不需要一個浪費時間去捨命搶廢紙的人。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#4$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那時源石液洩漏了，我先判斷了緊急情況——", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你要判斷的是實驗數據的價值。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#4$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則做這樣的決定就只是衝動。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#4$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有空多走出實驗室想想。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "支撐你做決定的應該是更長遠的目光和更卓越的見識，它們讓你看到了一個值得忽略性命的結果，而不是“沒想那麼多”。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了......謝謝主任的指導。以後我會先判斷結果是否值得再做決定，不會再衝動。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主任，如果在那種環境下，我判斷出它是很有價值的數據呢？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南收回看向外面的目光。"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他看向埃琳娜。"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜正仰著頭，如同每一個渴求他教導的學生那樣，直直地看向他的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南微笑起來。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是我，我會更晚一點拉響警報。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可——？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南抬手看了看錶，打斷了她要說的話。"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些人也是需要提前判斷的東西。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......七分鐘。文件給你，拿好了。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我明白了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我已經整理好了上次實驗所剩下的數據和相關報告，會儘快完成交接工作。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figu